<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link173462" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=173462&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F366778-does-anyone-know-why-yvonne-s-letters-all%2Fanswers%2F173462-i-had-the-impression">flag</a>
